Definition: law) a conference held before the trial begins to bring the parties together to outline discovery proceedings and to define the issues to be tried
Example: more useful in civil than in criminal cases
Synonyms: pretrial_conference, conference, noun, group, law, c, a, held, before, the, trial, begins, to, bring, parties, together, outline, discovery, proceedings, and, define, issues, be, tried, more, useful, in, civil, than, criminal, cases
Category: noun.communication
